						               													<description>IT IS A TIME OF DECISION!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Summer 1941&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Will you relive or will you reshape history?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The stakes are high as you take your role as a leader of a great power in the darkest days of the 20th Century. The scene is set, will the Axis launch Barbarossa, the greatest military campaign in history, which set the course for the rest of the Second World War? You can sit on the sideline and watch as world events occur. You can co-operate with other players to defend and develop your lands, or you can trust no one but yourself, as you build up your power and influence around the globe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Interact with your friends in 5 dimensions in this realistic civilization game, as you build up your strength using different resources and skills to gain advantage.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Set your heart and mind on one or more of the 5 dimensions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;MILITARY WAR: Great land, sea and air battles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ECONOMIC CRISIS: Struggle for strategic resources and economic growth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;DIPLOMATIC PRESSURE: Coerce or persuade new nations into trade or war.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;TECHNOLOGY RACE: Develop new weapons or industrial production breakthroughs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;MORAL CONFLICT: Join the eternal battle between good and evil.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How will you guide your power?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This inspiring game can be played in either a co-operative or non-co-operative way. In this fast moving non-turn based educational game, opportunities are continuously presented to make decisions and act. The rules you need to play are not difficult but to master the dimensions many skills are needed. Each dimension is learned one at a time and the rules are written to allow players to gradually add more dimensions. As the intricacy increases with added dimensions, you will enjoy the growing challenge to plan more strategically, think more long-term and more effectively leverage the inter dependency of the dimensions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;REALITY CHANGE GAME&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As you take your path through the seasons and steps of this challenging lost world, it is like your walk through life, making decisions and developing new people and mind skills and even heart change. The challenge to grow in strength in the game, encourages learning in critical thinking and problem solving, in team work, negotiation, and strategy, which can change the attitudes and thoughts of both your mind and heart.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Write to info@playfordgames.com on the Playford Games web site to receive the improved 2019 rule book.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Complete with an extra strategy guide that provides inspiration and ideas to equip to survive the game and succeed in  your every day conflict when the game is over.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
